      "text": "The [[collaborative link]] is a significant innovation in hypertext thinking. It provides a mechanism for texts to find each other which is engineered from a social perspective rather than a technical or media perspective. Your link finds pages that make contextual sense, rather than a simple fixed reference which takes you to the same place regardless of context."
